"ඔබ තවමත් එසේ කර නැත්නම්, ඔබගේ ටිකට්පත මෙහි බාගත කළ හැක:\n"
"{url}\n"
"\n"
"සුභ පැතුම්,\n"
"ඔබගේ {event} කණ්ඩායම"

#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:2003
#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:2012
#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:2027
#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:2037
#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:2052
#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:2062
#: base/configurations/default_setting.py:2077
